metadata.name: My Wistful Tragedies
metadata.description:
Running away...  
Still figuring out where to!  
I am constantly strangled by my own chains of thoughts;  
My own traumas of self-suffocation...  
The turmoils have been chasing me since I could sense pain.  
I lost my reflection, I lost my shadow-  
I lost myself- once again...  
My forever blue.
